# {{military}} Any combination of characters or pronounceable words, which identifies a communication facility, a [[command]], an [[authority]], an [[activity]], or a [[unit]]; used primarily for [[establishing]] and [[maintaining]] [[communications]]. Also called [[CS]]. (JP 1-02 Department of Defense Dictionary of Military and Associated Terms.)
##'''''CHARLIE PAPA'''''
##'''''D6P'''''
# (''broadcasting'') A combination of letters used to identify a radio or television station.

